<view class="mk-page">
  <view class="mk-title">保存你的餐厅经营档案</view>
  <view class="mk-sub">不是注册账号——绑定手机后，报告与档案可跨端同步到经营大脑。</view>

  <view class="mk-card">
    <view class="mk-field-label">手机号</view>
    <input class="mk-input" type="number" maxlength="11" placeholder="11 位手机号" value="{{phone}}" bindinput="onPhone" />
    <button class="mk-btn" bindtap="onSave">确认保存</button>
  </view>
</view>
